{"tid":2176811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該以後唔好叫「警方」、「警察」","createTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T10:50:10.000Z","uid":268677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"59a8815a17470a9ff0eceb4a2502c3f204830bfe","tid":2176811,"uid":268677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:00.000Z","msg":"「警方」「警察」係官方嘅叫法。有時出鏡或接受訪問，冇辦法，用詞要斯文d, 就叫左呢d 官方叫法。除左叫佢地9、黑警，佢地都好唔鐘意俾人叫「差佬」。因為「差佬」兩個字，表示左佢地好求其、爛仔、唔專業、低下階層。所以，以後出鏡或接受訪問，要斯文d稱呼班狗，一定要叫佢地做「差佬」！"},{"pid":"af98133a648449c09181dc340aff490d8b5f41fc","tid":2176811,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:20.000Z","msg":"死差佬"},{"pid":"6875e325baebaf1f83e46906979baa4b360cf23c","tid":2176811,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"叫開狗賊"},{"pid":"ec0e45757b8a0cdb6ab05d4dc746b3fc654b539c","tid":2176811,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:07:36.000Z","msg":"要改口咪叫呀sir喇 ..."},{"pid":"54d5504943fae39b740c8946a3bb2eccf4c95464","tid":2176811,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6875e325baebaf1f83e46906979baa4b360cf23c","tid":2176811,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"叫開狗賊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲叫曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫撚到班藍絲廢老濛撚左"},{"pid":"9ac22c8f84a5024ea57205d7de9eb66a562caa2f","tid":2176811,"uid":339751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"我一向叫開狗 就算出街俾狗逗<br />\n我都會叫佢地做狗 香港冇侮警罪<br />\n叫狗又點？唔通佢地埋嚟咬我咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74de7ced5ccf8969952c93a872c1a012fea974ce","tid":2176811,"uid":339751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/fa